<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Supple Scale Armband - AC 3</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/wrists.shtml">Wrists</a><BR>
Weight: 0.1 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/cleric/armour/wrists.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/druid/armour/wrists.shtml">DRU</a>, <a href="/enchanter/armour/wrists.shtml">ENC</a>, <a href="/magician/armour/wrists.shtml">MAG</a>, <a href="/necromancer/armour/wrists.shtml">NEC</a>, <a href="/shaman/armour/wrists.shtml">SHM</a>, <a href="/wizard/armour/wrists.shtml">WIZ</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(INT +5) (WIS +5) (Sv Fire +10) (Mana +25) </font>
<BR>

